com.warpww.util

Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.warpww.util.Command

  • public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    Command is an incomplete object that is intended to wrap database calls. It includes calss to create JSON Commands, parse responses, etc. All designed to interact with the dao.dbProcess servlet.
    Since:
    2018.06.30 ***************************************************************************
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Warp Worldwide, LLC
